OL,3,CArsonist staged rooftop standoff after
OL,4,Csetting man on fire
OL,6,FAn arsonist who is already serving a
OL,7,Fprison sentence following a nine-hour
OL,8,Frooftop standoff with police has been
OL,9,Fjailed for setting a man alight as he
OL,10,Ftried to escape a flat fire.
OL,12,FRyan Tomney, 29, was locked up for
OL,13,Fseven years in 2023 for an offence of
OL,14,Faffray after taking to the roof of a
OL,15,Fproperty in Lincoln Boulevard, Grimsby.
OL,17,FSeveral homes were evacuated and a
OL,18,Fnumber of vehicles and houses were
OL,19,Fdamaged as Tomney threw bricks at
OL,20,Fpolice during the incident on 28 April
OL,21,F2022.
