OL,3,CArsonist staged rooftop standoff after
OL,4,Csetting man on fire
OL,6,FHe had scaled the building as officers
OL,7,Ftried to arrest him over an incident
OL,8,Ffour days earlier, when he set fire to
OL,9,Fa man as he fled a flat at St Luke's
OL,10,FCourt, in Heneage Road, Grimsby.
OL,12,FHull Crown Court heard Tomney had
OL,13,Fstarted a fire in the flat and then
OL,14,Fset the victim's BMW alight.
OL,16,FA woman who was staying with the
OL,17,Fvictim raised the alarm and he emerged
OL,18,Ffrom his flat wearing only his boxer
OL,19,Fshorts.
