OL,3,CArsonist staged rooftop standoff after
OL,4,Csetting man on fire
OL,6,FTomney then doused the 51-year-old man
OL,7,Fin flammable liquid and set him alight
OL,8,Fas he tried to get out.
OL,10,FA number of residents poured water
OL,11,Fover the victim in an attempt to put
OL,12,Fthe fire out.
OL,14,FThe victim sufferd 30% burns and spent
OL,15,Ffive days in intensive care. He had
OL,16,Fsubsequently died from unrelated
OL,17,Fcauses, the court heard.
