OL,3,CArsonist staged rooftop standoff after
OL,4,Csetting man on fire
OL,6,FTomney, of Normandy Road in
OL,7,FCleethorpes, pleaded guilty to causing
OL,8,Fgrievous bodily harm and arson with
OL,9,Fintent to danger life.
OL,11,FHe was given a life sentence with a
OL,12,Fminimum term of eight years.
OL,14,FJudge John Thackray KC said CCTV
OL,15,Ffootage of the incident was "horrific
OL,16,Fto watch".
