OL,3,CArsonist staged rooftop standoff after
OL,4,Csetting man on fire
OL,6,F"It must have been terrifying for him
OL,7,Fand his female friend. It caused
OL,8,Fhorrendous injuries and you made the
OL,9,Fremainder of his life a misery. He was
OL,10,Fin significant pain."
OL,12,FDet Con Scott Jackson, of Humberside
OL,13,FPolice, said: "Tomney is a violent
OL,14,Findividual who attended the flat with
OL,15,Fone motive ` to cause significant harm.
OL,17,F"The value of damage caused to the
OL,18,Fflat at St Luke's Court totalled over
OL,19,F#15,000, but that is nothing compared
OL,20,Fto the suffering caused to the man
OL,21,Finjured in the incident."
